00:19:37,125 --> 00:19:39,458
And the ones I couldn't play,
I researched online.

495
00:19:39,541 --> 00:19:41,583
Bet you recognize this move,

496
00:19:41,666 --> 00:19:42,833
don't you, Miyamo?

497
00:19:42,916 --> 00:19:44,416
[MASAOMI]
I love you, Shouhei.

498
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:46,166
I can do this!

499
00:19:46,250 --> 00:19:47,833
[ANDOU]
The foot slam is a classic move

500
00:19:47,916 --> 00:19:50,916
from a wildly popular
game called <i>Endor</i> .

501
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:54,250
I even got my buddy
to help me out.

502
00:19:54,333 --> 00:19:56,708
[ANDOU] You're the only
one I trust, man!

503
00:19:56,791 --> 00:19:59,000
'Kay fine, just
because it's you.

504
00:19:59,083 --> 00:20:01,000
You sure you want me to do this?

505
00:20:01,083 --> 00:20:03,125
Yeah, put all your
weight on top-a me.

506
00:20:03,208 --> 00:20:06,750
[BOTH groaning]

507
00:20:06,833 --> 00:20:08,041
[ANDOU]
I got this.

508
00:20:08,125 --> 00:20:10,083
It'll all be worth it!

509
00:20:10,166 --> 00:20:12,625
Omigod isn't that the super-hot
foot slam from <i>Endor</i> ?

510
00:20:12,708 --> 00:20:14,541
I love BL games so much!

511
00:20:14,625 --> 00:20:17,250
[ANDOU]
Just to see her smile...

512
00:20:17,333 --> 00:20:20,833
[ALL groaning]

513
00:20:24,041 --> 00:20:26,375
[ANDOU]
Please. Recognize it!

514
00:20:26,458 --> 00:20:28,583
Hurry!

515
00:20:28,666 --> 00:20:29,666
[whispers] Manana.

516
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:31,458
What exactly are we looking at?

517
00:20:31,541 --> 00:20:33,208
[MANANA gulps]

518
00:20:33,291 --> 00:20:34,750
Nice to see you again.

519
00:20:34,833 --> 00:20:37,166
I'd like you to
meet my boyfriend.

520
00:20:37,250 --> 00:20:38,833
We're so in love
and we don't care...

521
00:20:38,916 --> 00:20:40,416
[MANANA]
...who knows about us either.

522
00:20:40,500 --> 00:20:43,958
Also, did you happen to notice
how flexible my legs are?

523
00:20:44,041 --> 00:20:45,291
Holy crap!

524
00:20:45,375 --> 00:20:47,250
[MANANA] Yeah, that's totally
what's goin' down.

525
00:20:47,333 --> 00:20:49,166
[MANANA] 'Kay, well don't
wanna interrupt.

526
00:20:49,250 --> 00:20:50,833
--[CHIO] See ya later.
--[ANDOU gasps]

527
00:20:50,916 --> 00:20:52,166
What? Hold on!

528
00:20:52,250 --> 00:20:53,833
Wasn't that the foot
slam from <i>Endor</i> ?!

529
00:20:53,916 --> 00:20:55,000
[GIRL squeals]

530
00:20:58,166 --> 00:21:00,791
I mean, they're already
into it this early?

531
00:21:00,875 --> 00:21:02,666
Makes sense now why we
kept running into him.

532
00:21:02,750 --> 00:21:04,416
His boyfriend must live
around here somewhere.

533
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:08,333
What? Your face got all tragic.

534
00:21:09,416 --> 00:21:12,125
[CHIO]
I just feel stupid.

535
