This whole time
I was thinking...

536
00:21:14,708 --> 00:21:17,666
...maybe Andou actually
liked me because, well--

537
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:19,500
Gah! I'm such an idiot!

538
00:21:19,583 --> 00:21:22,416
Why would anyone be
into someone like me?

539
00:21:22,500 --> 00:21:24,500
There's at least one
person who digs on you.

540
00:21:24,583 --> 00:21:25,541
[CHIO]
No there's not!

541
00:21:25,625 --> 00:21:27,083
Unless they're blind
and desperate!

542
00:21:27,166 --> 00:21:29,083
I'm so humiliated!

543
00:21:29,166 --> 00:21:30,583
I'm sure that's not true.

544
00:21:30,666 --> 00:21:32,625
Trust.

545
00:21:32,708 --> 00:21:33,791
[ANDOU]
Damn it!

546
00:21:33,875 --> 00:21:35,750
How the hell did I manage
to mess that up?

547
00:21:35,833 --> 00:21:36,791
This sucks!

548
00:21:36,875 --> 00:21:38,375
I'm sorry about that, man.

549
00:21:38,458 --> 00:21:40,041
I know this was
awkward for you.

550
00:21:40,125 --> 00:21:41,416
It's fine.

551
00:21:41,500 --> 00:21:44,166
Actually, I kind of enjoyed
playing your boyfriend.

552
00:21:44,250 --> 00:21:46,458
[ANDOU gasps]

553
00:21:46,541 --> 00:21:49,166
[MANANA]
<i>Chio's School Road</i> ! Bam!

554
00:21:49,250 --> 00:21:52,750
She gave me her email address;
that has to be a sign!

555
00:21:52,833 --> 00:21:55,375
Today I'll man up and
ask her on a date!

556
00:21:55,458 --> 00:21:58,375
Not too forward, but still
a clear invitation.

557
00:21:58,458 --> 00:22:00,625
At least I hope.
I guess we'll see.

558
00:22:00,708 --> 00:22:02,041
[CHIO] If you consider
the cost and value,

559
00:22:02,125 --> 00:22:03,916
you're actually better off
if you chomp on some juice

560
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:05,000
you chilled in the freezer.

561
00:22:05,083 --> 00:22:06,958
She rejected me!

562
00:23:37,541 --> 00:23:39,333
[YUKI] Next time on
<i>Chio's School Road</i> !

563
00:23:39,416 --> 00:23:42,250
"Shinozuka, Sugar Content,
and the Press Conference."

564
00:23:42,333 --> 00:23:44,750
"Thousand Spring,"
and "Andou and George."

565
00:23:44,833 --> 00:23:46,791
Hope you're ready
for a real head rush.

